			<h2 id="intl">Help Make The Site International</h2>
			<p>Are you an international fan of Shark Week? Right now, IsItSharkWeek.com only represents English-speaking visitors and the US dates for Shark Week. With your help, we can make the site for everyone. If you're an international fan and want to volunteer to update the site for your region, <a href="mailto:hammerhead@isitsharkweek.com?subject="International_Fan">send us an email</a>.</p>
